  <h2>Chapter 1: Real Numbers</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>The HCF of 36 and 48 is:  
      <div class="options">a) 6 &nbsp;&nbsp; b) 12 &nbsp;&nbsp; c) 18 &nbsp;&nbsp; d) 24</div>
